============================================================================

This file contains the ASCII-armored PUBLIC half of the GPG key used to
sign release artifacts (the SHA256SUMS file shipped alongside every tagged
release archive). It satisfies FR-015 by making the signing key
discoverable directly from the repository root.

Cross-check the fingerprint below against any other channel (commit history,
release notes, README) BEFORE importing the key. Never import a key that
arrives in a single source you cannot independently verify.

